  "texts": [
    "For instance, if one non-human agent (e.g.",
    "a generative AI) does not have guardrails for preventing the generation of content denying the Holocaust, whereas another similar agent does, then different logics may enter the conflict.",
    "Similar conflicts may also occur between robotic agents processing memory-related information about individuals.",
    "An example of this is the situation where two AI systems have to assess their human owner's health using historical information from different smart sensors and interpret the data from these sensors in a different way.",
    "This lack of transparency is particularly concerning due to the epistemic uncertainty about the consequences of robotic agents proactively engaging in memory communication with each other."
  ],
